name: Waste Oil Collection Direct Sales YTD
query:
select sl.name as "Receipt:Data:100",sl.posting_date as "Date:Date:100",sl.supplier as "Supplier:Data:200",itm.item_name as "Item:Data:150",sl.total as "Net :Float:100",sl.total_taxes_and_charges as "Tax:Float:100",sl.grand_total as "Grand Total:Float:100",sl.total_qty  as "Qty:Int:100"
			from `tabPurchase Receipt` sl left join `tabPurchase Receipt Item` itm on itm.parent=sl.name where 
			sl.company='Dure Oil Middle East Factory - Sole Proprietorship LLC'  and itm.item_code='wo005'
			and YEAR(sl.posting_date) = YEAR(CURRENT_DATE()) and sl.docstatus=1 group by sl.name
report_name: Waste Oil Collection Direct Sales YTD
